https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Form_validation

input uncommon attributes:

readonly
disabled
placeholder
size
spellcheck
required
minlength / maxlength -- strings
min/max -- nums 
pattern // regExp
autocomplete="[name]"


input type = "file" // chooses file

pseudo-elements:

:required;
:optional;
:valid
:invalid
:in-range
:out-of-range
:enabled
:disabled
:read-only
:read-write
:checked
:indeterminate
:default


for regex : https://www.html5pattern.com/

Characters

Escape character: \
Any character: .
Digit: \d
Not a digit: \D
Word character: \w
Not a word character: \W
Whitespace: \s
Not whitespace: \S
Word boundary: \b
Not a word boundary: \B
Beginning of a string: ^
End of a string: $



Groupings

Matches characters in brackets: [ ]
Matches characters not in brackets: [^ ]
Either or: |
Capturing group: ( )



Quantifiers

0 or more: *
1 or more: +
0 or 1: ?
An exact number of characters: { }
Range of number of characters: {Minimum, Maximum}